[[[description]]]
Accesses (either for setting or retrieval) the reference count of a type.

It must only be used on reference-counted types, such as [`zend_string`](https://phpinternals.net/docs/zend_string) and [`HashTable`](https://phpinternals.net/docs/hashtable).

